column5: What a nice day to be out . Me and a friend worked all day, Moving around  from 9 till 3 before we got into fish then our last shot caught these  all in 35 min  and went home .. I have been eating a lot of whitie  lol...  ill be out again tomorow ...
a beautiful day for sure , i was working outside for most of it ,, wishin' i was on the ice instead. great you got out and got a few on the ice ,, congrats.
Very jelous. Hard work pay off, last 35min of 6 hrs of fishing. Any tips for someone who havnt caught their first whitie yet?
